Description: Tools to download global and European geospatial data from
    Eurostat's GISCO (Geographic Information System of the Commission)
    geodata distribution <https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/gisco>. The
    package provides helpers for working with country boundaries, NUTS
    regions, administrative and statistical units, transport networks,
    basic services and other GISCO datasets. This package is not
    officially related to or endorsed by Eurostat.
License: GPL-3
